[normal]1.2.
[normal]&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0; 
[normal]The Big Lottery Fund has 
[normal]supported 
[normal]a wealth of projects 
[normal]and organisations that 
[normal]seek to combat youth 
[normal]unemployment
[normal] across the UK
[normal]. 
[normal]We have made awards worth around £300
[normal] 
[normal]million 
[normal]to projects supporting young people, 
[normal]ranging from small community based grants to large investments in national VCSE organisations. 
[normal]&#xa0;
[normal]1.3.
[normal]&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0; 
[normal]Many of our initiatives are targeted at young 
[normal]people who are not in education, employment or training or those moving from education to full-time work.
[normal] 
[normal]In supporting young peopl
[normal]e the Fund
[normal] has also found that there is a particular need to support young people experiencing challenging life transitions, 
[normal]such as leaving care or young offenders. All our investments focus on hard to reach young people and some focus on specific groups that require dedicated support, including young carers, young people leaving care and young people leaving youth offending in
[normal]stitutions.
